org.sabre.utils

Class CharsetMapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sabre.utils.CharsetMapper

  • public class CharsetMapper
extends java.lang.Object
    Purpose of the class is to provide a default implementation of the datacoding scheme mapping . If necessary different protocols can override the implementation of the function
